%h2 Other visitors
%p.hidden--js-enabled You can have up to 2 adults (over 18) and 3 children visiting at the same time. Seats are provided only for adults, so children may have to sit on your lap. 
%p.visible--js-enabled You can have up to 3 adults (over 18) and 3 children visiting at the same time. Seats are provided only for adults, so children may have to sit on your lap.

.group.group--inline.visible--js-enabled
  %label(for="number_of_adults") How many other visitors?
  = select_tag 'visit[visitor][][number_of_adults]', options_for_select([['none',0],1,2,3,4,5], v.number_of_adults.to_s), :class => 'number_of_visitors adults'
